text: Franny's Feet was a 2003-10 Canadian children's animated educational television series produced by CBC Productions, Discovery Kids Original, RD Denmark, Discovery Kids Latin America, and Discovery Kids Brazil. It was made its debut in 2003. The series was ended in 2012.
